('C1', 4020, $$Enfase com so / such$$, $$so tired / such a day$$, $$❗$$,
$$Para intensificar: SO + adjetivo/adverbio (so tired, so quickly). SUCH + (a/an) + adjetivo + substantivo (such a nice day, such good food). Uncountable/plural nao leva a/an: such nice weather.$$,
$$so = com adjetivo sozinho; such = quando ha substantivo.$$,
$j$[{"en": "It was so cold.", "pt": "Estava tao frio."}, {"en": "It was such a cold day.", "pt": "Foi um dia tao frio."}, {"en": "They have such nice ideas.", "pt": "Eles tem ideias tao boas."}]$j$::jsonb,
