('C1', 4023, $$Prefixos negativos$$, $$un- / dis- / mis- / over-$$, $$➖$$,
$$Prefixos mudam sentido: un- (unhappy, unfair), in-/im-/ir- (impossible, irregular), dis- (disagree, dishonest), mis- (misunderstand = entender errado), over- (overwork = trabalhar demais), under- (underestimate = subestimar).$$,
